utterance_text: I don't know what to do. I've tried to quit smoking. I've had, uh, I've taken pills, I've taken the patch.

utterance_text: So it's hard for you to quit smoking when everybody else around you is smoking. And it's so easy to go out and take a break and have a cigarette.
